title: Videos, photos: Social media capture haunting views of south Louisiana tornadoes
text:
10 min ago ( â€¦ ) 
Advocate staff photo by SOPHIA GERMER -- Severe weather damage in New Orleans East on Tuesday, Feb. 7, 2017. Advocate staff photo by MATTHEW HINTON 
Tornado damage is seen on Knight Drive in New Orleans East, La. Tuesday, Feb. 7, 2017. TownNews.com Content Exchange 
Tornadoes ripped through south Louisiana on Monday, hitting eastern New Orleans, Killian and Donaldsonville particularly hard. 
Dozens of photos and videos posted on social media captured the devastating power of the storms.
